	   <tr><td colspan=2>Go to dalnir and find a good group(chanter + tank are a MUST). Camp the imp room and pull into there.  You can time it so the imp doesnt pop during your pulls(he or his ph pops every 13 minutes like everything else in dalnir). You should be getting close to one yellow bar per hour with constant pulls in there, even at hell level.  Plus the lumpys will give you the practice sword and batons for $$, and if your chanter is extremely lucky you will get the dalnir robe.  <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
