	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Specialization gives you a chance to reduce the fizzle rate and mana cost in a particular casting discipline. It doesn't work all the time, but when it does it can really cut down on downtime. You can get four of your discipline specializations up to 50, and one (the first to hit 51) will raise much, much higher.<br><br>Almost all clerics choose Alteration as their main specialization, since healing is their primary occupation.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
