<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=98811007047332></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f98811007047332><tr><td id=headerrow><span id=sj><a href=/strategy/classes.html?class=7&mid=98811007047332>RE: Are clerics better then paladins?</a></span></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
