	   <tr><td colspan=2><br>Regarding weight, I regularly group with an Enchanter who was nice enough to make me some STR jewelry. That really helped at lower levels. I also will use the Yaulp line of spells when running to the bank encumbered. This is the only use I have found for this line of spells. It gives you a STR boost for a short amount of time. <br><br>Another trick I use is to drop copper in increments of 40 since 40 copper seems to be about 1 stone. So just drop 40 copper if you need to shed one quick pound.<br><br>The thing that has helped me the most was getting a Sewn Bag of Evil Eye out of LGuk. A very nice 8 slot 70% weight reducing bag. Granted, you can't get it until about 30 with a full group. If you have never killed a Frog then you can walk all the way to the spawn spot without even fighting. The spawn time is about 30 minutes with a Shaman place holder every now and then. Very easy quest for a very nice item.<br><br>Andav<br>Madcap Cleric of 30 Seasons<br>Tunare Server<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
