	   <tr><td colspan=2>This partly depends on your level.  At lower levels mana is better than Wisdom.  For example the 6 Wisdom rings are don't give 30 mana till level 25, so up to level 25 + 30 mana is better, at lvl 25 both are equal, past lvl 25 =6 WIS is better.  EXCEPT, the +30 mana gives +3 STR which you may need AND if you are already at 200 WIS adding more WIS does not give you as much more mana as it does below 200.<br><br>Alot of equipment has multiple stats, +5sv cold may be more important to you during a Vox Raid than the extra mana from another piece of equipment.  May people dump alot of equipment to replace it with Splitpaw hide armor when they go to fight Trakanon.  <br><br>Wisdom vs Mana - depends on the situation<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
